	   <tr><td colspan=2>theres a couple of tricks i read to help keep your trader online which seems to work for me.<br><br>First, turn badword filter on. type /filter badword.<br><br>second, turn clip planes and all graphic settings to minimum.<br><br>third, turn off all ooc chat auctions etc. i read that theres a problem with oocing item links which can cause crashes. <br><br>Before i did this i woudlnt last a night with my trader, now hes on pretty much full time.<br><br>Gulug<br>63 Warlord<br><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
