	   <tr><td colspan=2>Look into Timorous Deep, find Golra island, Single spawn Monkeys , No roamers, No adds ever, get ALOT of bandages, and start swimming... It's the safest exp there is, and you'll be good there for a couple more levels, at which point you can try to take on the &quot;Hulking Golra&quot;'s... which are lvl 35, I'm not sure if a warrior can solo them with half life and bandaging? But its worth a try, I'd say its your best bet, warriors arent a solo class... Better yet, find a shaman partner and drag him out there with you. Hope this helps, it's not your fault your french... :-)<br><br>Talon<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
