	   <tr><td colspan=2>I would suggest that you get some 1hs asap.&nbsp;&nbsp;Most of the best weapons for warrior are 1hs.  1hs and 1hb should be the first skills you lvl max.  Normally do the the damage caps you shouldn't use two hand weapons as your primary weapon until after lvl 20. <br>At your lvl regardless of the weapon's damage it will act as a 14 damage weapon.<br>There are more uber 2hs weapons for warrior than 2hb weapons and a number of warriors never develop their 2hb.  For this reason warrior only 2hbs are some of the cheepest weapons in the game.  If you can get a better 2hb than your current 2hs cheep (maybe a SBH) then I would skill up 2hb.  <br>Daggers and spears are the last weapons you should care about.  for one we have a lower skill max for these weapons.  Two at higher lvl the 1hb and 1hs are normally much better<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
