	   <tr><td colspan=2>Warrior are one of the hardest classes to solo.&nbsp;&nbsp;For me the key to warrior soloing are very high ac armor for lvl.  Weapons with high damage per second.  Bind wounds skill.<br>To solo effecntly as a warrior you need to be able to kill the mob with half or less of your hit points.  Then bind wounds to half (or just before you are nolonger beserk if you can spare a few hps in order to max damage output) and do it all over again.<br>If you have the plat there are items that improve regen or even heal.  <br>But in the end warriors need groups. Once you get to lvl 45 head over the the DL and see if you can't start getting into some groups.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
