	   <tr><td colspan=2>I have talked to a lot of different races and classes, and it comes down to this.&nbsp;&nbsp;Most find soloing difficult no matter what.  although there are the few out there who say they have soloed from level 1 to 60 with no problem.  (my hat goes off to them)<br><br>Soloing is slow and tedious for anyone, and you learn to just DO IT!  or you group.  It takes a lot of patience to solo at times.  I find most people do not have the patience for soloing and because of this, they die a lot, and spend too much time doing corpse recovery than gaining exp. This same impatience can be very dangerous when found in a group.  I have been killed faster in a group than I was ever killed soloing, because of someone's impatience.<br><br>I have soloed most of my career (level 20 now) and have become very adept at surviving solo.  Having said all that, I have been grouping as of lately, and I think this is the way to go, which is the way it was meant to be.  Sometimes we find ourselves in a situation where there is no one to group with, and we must go it alone.  Know your char's strenghts and weaknesses, and capitalize on the strenghts and gaurd against the weaknesses, or correct them.  <br><br>I would like to hear what others think about why so many whine about soloing being difficult.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
